macro index,pager i3 '<sync-mailbox><enter-command>source /home/otislevoll/.config/mutt/accounts/3-oveee92-hotmail.muttrc<enter><change-folder>!<enter>;<check-stats>' "switch to oveee92@hotmail.com" # mw-autogenerated
